memberOrga:
AMBER Alert Europe has 22 members in 16 countries, 6 of which are law enforcement organizations. Its police expert group exists of over 35 people from 12 countries. &#xd;
Its Board and Advisory Board are composed of a selection of independent experts from law enforcement, academia, civil service as well as civil society.&#xd;
&#xd;
It is the biggest European citizen sourced- initiative with 3 million participants across the European Union.
